<p>(RELX as an Alternative to Smoking: Harm Reduction and Considerations)</p>

<p>For many adults, the primary appeal of RELX and other <strong>e-cigarettes</strong> is as a potential <strong>alternative to smoking</strong>.  Public Health England and other organizations have stated that vaping is significantly less harmful than smoking traditional cigarettes [^1^]. While vaping is not risk-free, and long-term health effects are still being studied, it eliminates many of the harmful chemicals produced by burning tobacco.</p>

<p>RELX, with its nicotine salt formulation, aims to provide a satisfying nicotine experience that can help smokers transition away from cigarettes.  The reduced odor compared to cigarettes is another significant benefit appreciated by both users and those around them.</p>

<p>However, it’s crucial to understand that <strong>vaping</strong> is not harmless, and <strong>nicotine</strong> is an addictive substance.  RELX and other vaping products are intended for adult smokers seeking to switch, not for non-smokers or young people.  If you are a non-smoker, you should not start vaping.</p>

